    <h1 id="aboutUsHeading">About us</h1>
    <p id="aboutUsIntro">Welcome to Task hive, where we believe that effective task management is the key to unlocking your full potential. Our platform is designed to help you organize, prioritize, and streamline your tasks, whether you're an individual or part of a larger team. At TaskFlow, we're driven by a clear vision and mission that guide everything we do.</p>
    <h2>Our mission</h2>
    <p>At TaskHive, our mission is to revolutionize the way people manage their tasks and projects. We believe in the power of organization and efficiency to drive success and achieve goals. Our goal is to provide a seamless and intuitive platform that simplifies task management and enhances productivity for individuals and teams alike.</p>

    <h2>Our story</h2>
    <p>Founded in 2024, Taskhive was born out of a need for a more effective way to handle complex workflows and task lists. Our team of passionate professionals recognized the challenges people face when juggling multiple responsibilities and decided to create a solution that would make task management easier and more effective.</p>
